1. *Zbunjen* sam zbog tvojih postupaka. (I'm confused because of your actions.)
2. Njegova reakcija je bila potpuno *zbunjena*. (His reaction was completely bewildered.)
3. Ona je ostala *zbunjena* nakon što je čula loše vijesti. (She remained confused after hearing the bad news.)
4. *Zbunjenost* je bila očigledna na njenom licu. (Confusion was evident on her face.)
5. Njegovo ponašanje je ostavilo druge *zbunjene*. (His behavior left others bewildered.)
6. U ovom trenutku, ne želim ništa reći jer sam previše *zbunjen*. (At this moment, I don't want to say anything because I'm too confused.)
7. Njegov govor je bio pun *zbunjujućih* informacija. (His speech was full of confusing information.)
8. Kada je čula nepoznat glas, postala je jako *zbunjena*. (When she heard an unfamiliar voice, she became very confused.)
9. Bila je toliko *zbunjena* da nije mogla pronaći izlaz. (She was so confused that she couldn't find a way out.)
10. *Zbunjujuće* situacije su neizbježne u životu. (Confusing situations are inevitable in life.)